OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fcontinue through the evening,
OL,7,Fgenerally becoming light and more
OL,8,Fisolated although the Pennines likely
OL,9,Fstill seeing some heavier bursts.
OL,10,FShowers easing off around midnight
OL,11,Fwith some clear spells developing and
OL,12,Ffeeling cold. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FSunny spells and occasional
OL,15,Fshowers through the day, some of which
OL,16,Fcould be heavy and thundery. Clouding
OL,17,Fover from the west overnight as rain
OL,18,Fand stronger winds arrive.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
